@Backend_HostAddress = http://localhost:5047

### Register
POST {{Backend_HostAddress}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test3@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Login
POST {{Backend_HostAddress}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test3@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Me (replace {{accessToken}} with the token from Login response)
GET {{Backend_HostAddress}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###
